==國民議會選舉==
國民議會的140個席位由單議席選區選出，採用[[两轮选举制|两轮选举制]]，<ref name="ipu2059">{{Cite web |url=http://archive.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2059.htm |title=CENTRAL AFRICAN REPUBLIC Assemblée nationale (National Assembly) |website=ipu.org |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2018-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011072849/http://archive.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2059.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>有大約1,500位候選人角逐。<ref name=voa20201227/>

2020年12月27日首輪投票有58個選區因為安全問題未能舉行投票。2021年2月1日，中非憲法法院裁定另外13個選區因為有選舉違規而需要重新投票。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://news.yahoo.com/top-court-scraps-vote-results-172827384.html |title=Top court scraps vote results in 13 C.Africa constituencies |website=news.yahoo.com |date=2021-02-02 |accessdate=2021-02-05 |archive-date=2021-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210224708/https://news.yahoo.com/top-court-scraps-vote-results-172827384.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年3月14日，49個選區舉行國民議會選舉次輪投票，69個選區舉行首輪投票。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/central-african-republic-votes-amid-tight-security-after-december-violence |title=Central African Republic Votes amid Tight Security after December Violence |website=VOA |date=2021-03-14 |accessdate=2021-03-14 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320160551/https://www.voanews.com/africa/central-african-republic-votes-amid-tight-security-after-december-violence |dead-url=no }}</ref>

